      • addCue

        public MleCue addCue(MleCue cue)
              throws MleRuntimeException
        Add the Cue to the sheet.

        If the sheet previously contained a mapping for this cue, the old value is replaced.

        Parameters:
        cue - The cue to add.
        Returns:
        The previous cue associated with specified name will be returned. null will be returned if there was no mapping for the cue's name.
        Throws:
        MleRuntimeException - This exception is thrown if the input argument is null, the MleCue's name is null, or the MleCue's id is invalid.

      • removeCue

        public MleCue removeCue(java.lang.String name)
                 throws MleRuntimeException
        Remove the named Cue from the sheet.
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the Cue to remove.
        Returns:
        The previous cue associated with specified name will be returned. null will be returned if there was no mapping for the cue's name.
        Throws:
        MleRuntimeException - This exception is thrown if the input argument is null.

      • getCues

        public java.util.Collection<MleCue> getCues()
        Returns a collection view of the cues contained in this sheet. The collection is backed by the sheet, so changes to the sheet are reflected in the collection, and vice-versa. The collection supports element removal, which removes the corresponding mapping from this sheet.
        Returns:
        A collection view of the cues contained in this sheet is returned.
